The paper deals with the task of Visual Dialog, which involves natural language processing, computer vision, and machine learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper proposes a novel model that involves graphical models and neural networks, which are common techniques in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with the task of reasoning, which is a fundamental aspect of artificial intelligence and can be related to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
